# =============================================================================
# PRJ-019 Clawbridge — standalone repo root .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# 親 monorepo claude-code-company から detach した独立 repo として運用
# (DEC-019-053 v15.2 / Plan A 採択 2026-05-04)
# =============================================================================

# ---- Node / pnpm ----
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ---- Coverage / Test artifacts ----
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/
**/.vitest-cache/
**/__tests__/.tmp/

# ---- TypeScript ----
*.tsbuildinfo

# ---- Env / secrets (Tier 1 真の secret は GitHub Actions Secrets / Vault 管理) ----
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
.doppler/
.vault-token
**/.doppler/
**/.vault-token

# ---- Local Clawbridge runtime state ----
.clawbridge/
**/.clawbridge/

# ---- Open Claw vendor (CB-D-W0-04 で clone する上流リポ、再現可能なので除外) ----
**/openclaw-runtime/upstream/
**/openclaw-runtime/vendor/

# ---- Editor / OS ----
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ---- Misc ----
*.tmp
*.bak
